{"type": "article", "id": 4959, "title": "甜甜圈帐篷", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-06T07:58:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233522C3EDAnWQc4ermJYO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t帐篷能玩出什么花样？三位来自韩国的设计师 Sungha Lim、Hyunmook Lim 与 Han Kim 日前就带来了一款特别的甜甜圈帐篷 Camping Doughnut 。它其实就是一个圆柱状的超大型袋子，平日里不需要用时可以将其卷起来收纳，需要用的时候就能够将其变成圆柱状的搭帐篷，既可以将其凹成 S 形，也可以凹成 O 形，围成 O 形时，内部的封闭空地还可以转换成为小型的游戏区域，非常适合三五好友相约出行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233519dyCgrwOE5x6n8RZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233520U7tEybc1ZwWQa24s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233521QFl94nR5ELGCIsKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233521deMHr6XL0bkocGZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}